OL,6,FThe husband of a professional horse
OL,7,Frider who died while competing in
OL,8,FDevon has described her as "strong,
OL,9,Fbeautiful, and phenomenal".
OL,11,Fon Sunday 26 May.
OL,13,FThe 36-year-old represented Great
OL,14,FBritain numerous times on Nations Cup
OL,15,Fteams and appeared at several five-
OL,16,Fstar events - the highest recognised
OL,17,Flevel of eventing.
