OL,6,FCampbell married fellow equestrian
OL,7,FJesse Campbell, a member of the New
OL,8,FZealand team for the Tokyo Olympics,
OL,9,Fin December 2020.
OL,11,FJesse posted a tribute to his wife on
OL,12,FFacebook, saying "I love you so, so
OL,13,Fmuch" and referred to their wedding in
OL,14,F2021 as "the best day ever".
OL,16,FSharing a photo of his wife on their
OL,17,Fwedding day, he said: "People will
OL,18,Ftalk about G's smile, and it was
OL,19,Fincredible - it would make you feel
OL,20,Flike you were the centre of the
OL,21,Funiverse.
