OL,6,F"But what I love about this photo is
OL,7,Fhow it captures her strength. She was
OL,8,Fa strong, beautiful, phenomenal woman
OL,9,Fwho just loved everything and everyone.
OL,11,F"Working in the equestrian world is
OL,12,Fnot an easy life; there are a lot of
OL,13,Fknocks and dark days. But G would
OL,14,Fnavigate this by throwing so much joy
OL,15,Fand love at every situation.
