OL,4,C'phenomenal' rider who died competing
OL,6,F"She would get as much joy from having
OL,7,Fa Greggs tea on the way home from the
OL,8,Fgallops as she would teaching a client
OL,9,Fin the pouring rain or jumping and
OL,10,Fgalloping around biggest courses in
OL,11,Fthe world. It was just incredible to
OL,12,Fbe at your side and feel this energy.
OL,14,F"I'm so proud to be your husband. Rest
OL,15,Fin peace, my beautiful girl."
OL,17,FJesse praised the team at the horse
OL,18,Ftrials and thanked people for their
OL,19,Fsupport.
