OL,6,FHe said: "I don't want this to sound
OL,7,Flike a thank you speech, but there are
OL,8,Fsome people that I'd like to
OL,9,Facknowledge and thank.
OL,11,F"The team at Bicton, who were beyond
OL,12,Fwords in their care for Debbie, Diana,
OL,13,Fand me in the immediate aftermath;
OL,14,FTim, Jonelle, and their beautiful kids
OL,15,Ffor getting me through the first 24
OL,16,Fhours; and the Wolf Pack for being
OL,17,Fthere ever since.
