OL,6,F"There have been so many incredible
OL,7,Fmessages of support, and I'm sorry for
OL,8,Fnot getting back to more of you, but
OL,9,Fplease know that they have been read
OL,10,Fand are so appreciated.
OL,12,F"Seeing the purple and white ribbons
OL,13,Fhas been amazing.
OL,15,F"But on an even more basic level, when
OL,16,Fyou're out competing this weekend,
OL,17,Fplease just smile at each other, don't
OL,18,Ffeel awkward about laughing, and above
OL,19,Fall, try and love everything and
OL,20,Feveryone."
